Params: {1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: "I'm sure I don't have to introduce who we are collaborating with on this mission this time.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "I'll feel weird if that changes someday!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: "Haha! So will I! If I have to work with someone other than the Gray Ravens someday, I'm sure I'll be very disappointed!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: "It's time for me to show you how masterful I am now!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'You were already masterful—at diving right in without thinking.', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: "That wasn't diving in without thinking—it was bravery! Courage!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'We seem to disagree on what some of those words mean.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: 'I always feel like Lee gets to be a jerk because his frame is better designed and his database is bigger.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'The mood changes immediately with Kamui back.', 3: '24', 4: 'Look at how much livelier this is!', 5: '26'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: "I know I said it before, but as always, I'll do my best to work with you as a team! May the mission go smoothly!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'You feel more mature...', 3: '31', 4: "Seems like you've grown up!", 5: '31'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: "For sure! You don't get to make up those combat data from nothing, or calculate it with an algorithm!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: "That's how you can tell a Construct has grown!", 4: '1'}
